Class Actor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Delegator
      • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Actor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Creator, Deleter, Relator, Updater

    public abstract class Actor
extends Delegator
    LDP resource actor.

    Handles CRUD operations on linked data resources stored in the system graph and identified by the request focus item.

    • Method Detail

      • relate

        protected Collection<Statement> relate(IRI resource,
                                       Query query)
        Relates a resource.
        Parameters:
        resource - the IRI identifying the resource whose description is to be retrieved
        query - the query defining the details of resource to be retrieved;
        Returns:
        the description of resource matched by query; empty if a matching description for resource was not found; related resources matched by query are linked to resource with the ldp:contains property
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if either resource or query is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - if resource retrieval is not supported by this engine

      • create

        protected Optional<Focus> create(IRI resource,
                                 Shape shape,
                                 Collection<Statement> model)
        Creates a resource.
        Parameters:
        resource - the IRI identifying the resource whose description is to be created
        shape - the validation shape for the description of the resource;
        model - the description for resource to be created
        Returns:
        an optional validation report for the operation; empty a description for resource is already present
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if any argument is null or if model contains null values
        UnsupportedOperationException - if resource creation is not supported by this engine

      • update

        protected Optional<Focus> update(IRI resource,
                                 Shape shape,
                                 Collection<Statement> model)
        Updates a resource.
        Parameters:
        resource - the IRI identifying the resource whose description is to be updated
        shape - the validation shape for the description of the resource
        model - the updated description for resource
        Returns:
        an optional validation report for the operation; empty if a description for resource was not found
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if any argument is null or if model contains null values
        UnsupportedOperationException - if resource updating is not supported by this engine

      • delete

        protected Optional<Focus> delete(IRI resource,
                                 Shape shape)
        Deletes a resource.
        Parameters:
        resource - the IRI identifying the resource whose description is to be deleted
        shape - the validation shape for the description of the resource
        Returns:
        an optional IRI identifying the deleted resource; empty if a description for resource was not found
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if either resource or shape is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - if resource deletion is not supported by this engine
